('Turó Park Medical', 'Healthcare', 'Premium English-speaking healthcare clinic in Barcelona''s Sarrià-Sant Gervasi district. Over 40 highly-qualified international doctors and specialists providing comprehensive medical, dental, and aesthetic services. Medical clinic located at Plaça de Sant Gregori Taumaturg offering general medicine, pediatrics, gynecology, cardiology, dermatology, ENT (ear, nose, throat), physiotherapy, nutrition, infectious diseases, and specialist consultations. Dental clinic on Carrer Francesc Pérez Cabrero provides general dentistry, implants, orthodontics, and cosmetic dentistry. Full aesthetic medicine and cosmetic surgery services available. Open 7 days a week including holidays with emergency services available daily. Offers in-clinic appointments, online video consultations, and hotel/office/home visits for maximum convenience. All doctors, dentists, nurses, and administrative staff speak fluent English. Multilingual team also speaks Spanish, French, and other languages. Specialized in caring for expats, tourists, and international residents. Works with all major international insurance providers and provides invoices for reimbursement. American and English-speaking doctors experienced in diagnosing medical issues for international patients.', 'Plaça de Sant Gregori Taumaturg, 5, 08021 Barcelona', 'Barcelona', 'Barcelona', '+34 932 529 729', 'contact@turoparkmedical.com', 'https://turoparkmedical.com', true, true, true, false, NOW(), NOW());
